{
  "name": "纏爪刺青 Coiling Grasp Tattoo",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/tools/scribal/burnisher-tooth.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\">覆蓋區域：半條肢體或一整塊頭皮</p><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">該魔法刺青用一根特殊的針製作，繪有錯雜盤虬的圖案。</span><br /></p><ul><li><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">刺青同調。同調此物品時，你需要將針持握，並抵在你想要讓刺</span><span class=\"GramE\">青出現</span>的那處面板上。當同調完成時，針頭會化為墨水再變成刺青。若你與刺青的同調結束，刺青會消失，針頭會再次出現在你的位置中。</p></li><li><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">纏握觸鬚。當刺青在你的面板上時，你可以用一個動作讓刺青伸縮出一團能夠觸及一個</span>15<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺內你可見生物的墨黑色觸鬚。目標生物需要進行一次</span>DC14<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的力量豁免，豁免失敗則受到</span>3d6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">力場傷害並被你</span><em> </em><span class=\"GramE\"><em>擒抱</em></span><em>Grappled</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。作為一個動作，被擒抱的生物可以通過</span>DC14<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的力量（運動）或敏捷（體操）檢定以擺脫擒抱。在你使觸手停止（無需動作），或生物與你相距</span>15<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺以上或你對另一個生物使用此刺青時，</span><span class=\"GramE\">擒抱也會</span>結束。</p></li></ul></div></div>",
